{1: "That's the spark of civilization.", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '0.8', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 8: '1', 10: '1'}
{1: '???', 2: '000000ff', 3: '0', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '4', 10: '1'}
{1: 'The glory of the Golden Age will eventually spread across new lands.', 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '1.2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 8: '1', 10: '1'}
{1: '???', 2: '000000ff', 3: '0', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '4', 10: '1'}
{1: 'Only ▆▆▆▆ can take humanity back to Earth.', 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '1', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 8: '1', 10: '1'}
{1: '???', 2: '000000ff', 3: '0', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '4', 10: '1'}
{1: 'Christina, remember...', 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '0.8', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 8: '1', 10: '1'}
{1: '???', 2: '000000ff', 3: '0', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '4', 10: '1'}
{1: 'Only ▆▆▆▆...', 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '0.8', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 9: '1', 10: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory463.jpg'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "...Your dreams reflect your thoughts, huh? Can't believe I'm revisiting those memories after all this time...", 4: '1'}
{3: 'The terminal on the table persistently chimes for notifications.'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Are they finally on the move?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The slaughter between terminal networks is always hidden beneath a calm facade.'}

{3: 'It emerges silently, capturing information containing keywords, flickering like a firefly. Then it vanishes without a trace left behind, allowing the data streams to pass line by line through the firewall.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Inheritance... Are they seriously still holding on to a pointless belief like that?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Only those with brains infested by amoebas would keep on relying on those supposed geniuses from history...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The terminal displays a familiar name with a photo, where the once naive child has seemingly grown into someone who can handle herself well.'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "It's okay. It will come to an end.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Teddy...!'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory545.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "Hey, don't act like you're sleeping if you're awake! It's time for a meeting!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Another one, huh... Is there some action stirring up in the Hetero Zone?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'The military has retrieved... the last mission footage...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'The Hetero Zone is still expanding.', 4: '1'}
{1: 'DialogDisable'}
{1: 'Source Beacon', 2: 'Chapter 29', 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Atlas/CommonLogo/BgLogo1.png'}

{1: 'DialogEnable'}
{3: 'Something... is spreading...'}
{3: 'I see... red winds, green rains, purple soil, and heavy skulls...'}
{3: 'Vaguely human-like figures dissolve, dripping onto the barren land, emitting a sticky and unidentifiable fragrance.'}
{1: '1', 2: '????', 3: 'The history of mankind I have read and their civilization I have grasped. Now...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Embryos push through the muddied earth, blossoming into new flowers.'}
{2: '????', 3: "It's about to begin... This new story.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiDuihualiziEndRed.prefab', 2: '2'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiDuihualiziLoopRed.prefab'}
{3: 'Gurgle—'}
{3: 'A faint, subtle, low sound of bubbles popping mutes the final cry at the bottom of the throat.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory539.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Garry', 3: 'What was that sound?!', 4: '1'}
{3: "Upon hearing his warning, another refugee working in the woods abruptly halts his current task. He observes the grass that Garry is intently staring at, prepared to flee at a moment's notice."}
{3: 'Yet, after an extended wait, their eyes begin to swell and ache; all they perceive is the rustling of the wind through the trees.'}
{2: 'Garry', 3: 'I misheard it... probably.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Garry knocks his own head and shakes it in annoyance, feeling sorry for startling his friend at work.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gemira', 3: "It's okay. Being cautious is the right way to do things these days. Remember when that monster snuck up behind our camp? It was all thanks to your warning...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "Otherwise, even with Lucille's vehicles, we wouldn't have made it...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: 'Ahem, have you heard of the news?', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 3: 'He leans closer to Garry, speaking in a hushed voice.'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: 'You know that settlement near ours... the one back behind the woods that we outplayed in the turf scuffle before...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "Some told me this morning that when they went nearby to scavenge, they didn't hear a thing from that settlement.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Garry', 3: "They didn't go check it out?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "No one's got the nerve... These parts are nothing like the Clean Zone Lucille talked about.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Garry', 3: "But we've already scouted the surroundings...", 4: '1'}

{2: 'Gemira', 3: 'Nah, you crashed early last night, so you missed out on the update. Folks who bolted from the back a couple of days ago mentioned that... things are changing all the time over there.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "Seems like that Red Tide thing is still spreading. It catches you, and poof—you're gone in a blink!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "A few settlements have vanished already... I'm starting to worry we might have to move again soon.", 4: '2'}
{3: 'He lets out a sigh, pausing his work.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gemira', 3: "It's already December... Can we really make it through this winter?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Garry', 3: "Don't think like that.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Garry attempts to console him, but the words get stuck in his throat, uncertain of how to escape his lips.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory897.jpg'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Since that day—a date he has no way to confirm—everything seems to have subtly changed.'}
{3: 'These woods, most familiar to the refugees, seem to come "alive", breathing and thriving.'}
{3: "He can't quite pinpoint those subtle changes, but everything around him seems to be urging him to flee, to get out of this place."}
{3: 'But where can he go?'}
{3: 'Since the moment he became separated from his parents and had to fend for himself, there has been no turning back—he has to face this treacherous world on his own.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory346.jpg'}
{3: 'The Punishing Virus.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory547.jpg'}
{3: 'The Corrupted.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory614.jpg'}
{3: 'The Red Tide.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory767.png'}
{3: 'Those eerie-looking monsters referred to as Hetero-Creatures by the Constructs who always come and go hastily.'}
{3: 'And... even more unpredictable things.'}
{3: 'The refugees on the surface hide in the crevices of the world, barely surviving, while the monsters spawned by the Punishing Virus roam unrestrained.'}
{3: 'How much longer... can humans survive on this land?'}
{3: 'If not here... where else can they go?'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory539.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Garry', 3: "...Don't think like that.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'He only manages to squeeze out these pallid words.'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "...Sigh, you're right. Overthinking will do me no good.", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Rubbing his face nonchalantly, Gemira starts chuckling.'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "Things will get better... Lucille's already confirmed the location of the Clean Zone, hasn't he?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: 'Once we enter that Clean Zone she mentioned, things will definitely get better!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "She mentioned there's no sign of that damned virus in the Clean Zone and no chance of running into those monsters either.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "Once we're there, we'll set up our own homes and work the land—no more scavenging around for wild veggies to munch on.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "And then, hehe, let's get you a girlfriend... Do you like kids?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: 'Oh, I just love kids!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "If only my wife and I hadn't been split up ages ago. Too bad you can't meet her in person. Gotta admit, she's a stunner...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: 'When I first laid eyes on her, those big bright eyes of hers got me thinking, "If our kids could have eyes like that..."', 4: '2'}
{3: 'As Gemira rambles on, Garry finds himself lost in thoughts.'}
{3: 'He has never imagined a future like that.'}
{3: 'Where he might get a girlfriend, a place to call home, and perhaps even... a child.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png'}
{3: 'Child—'}
{3: 'Gurgle—'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory539.jpg'}
{1: '1', 3: 'An uneasy rustle emanates from the bushes.'}
{3: 'They pause their work once more with a glimmer of hope shining in their hearts, listening intently to the sounds around them.'}
{3: 'A subtle tremor ripples beneath their feet as if a herd of antelope is being pursued by wild beasts. Accompanied by this, chaotic footsteps draw closer almost instantly...'}
{3: "Garry's voice almost perfectly merges with that of the refugee fleeing from the bushes."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gemira', 3: "Wh-what's happening...?!", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory545.jpg'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Construct Soldier', 3: '...The Hetero Zone is still expanding...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Construct Soldier', 3: '...The last... data...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiNoiseNew.prefab'}

{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiHuaping.prefab'}
{1: '1', 3: 'The video flickers a few times before the recording abruptly cuts off.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nikola', 3: 'This is the last mission footage uploaded by this Construct squad.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nikola', 3: 'By the time we attempted to track them down, the Red Tide had already swept over the area.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nikola', 3: 'The task for this Construct squad involved eradicating the Hetero-Creatures on the outskirts of the Clean Zone. The mission location is very close to the Clean Zone.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nikola', 3: "The Hetero Zone is encroaching on the Clean Zone's territory.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nikola', 3: 'In places unknown to us...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The Red Tide is devouring more lives.'}
{3: 'It voraciously absorbs anything that can sustain itself—be it animals, plants, humans, or Constructs.'}
{3: 'It clusters tightly together, embracing as many lives as they can.'}
{3: 'It seems to intent on dragging the entire world into the nightmare it has weaved.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryWhiteNew.prefab', 2: '3'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory743.jpg'}
{3: "Winds as red as blood, rains as green as algae, and soil tainted with an ominous purple hue... they bear the cries of refugees who couldn't flee the woods."}
{3: 'Crimson liquid meanders like a stream, joyfully coursing through the crevices in the woods.'}
{3: 'Vines, reeking of decay, silently creep from the stream beyond, while the once-tranquil forest is now engulfed by screams, only to fall into an eerie silence again.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Garry', 3: "It's the Red Tide! Gemira! Run!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Desperately, Garry pulls Gemira along, sprinting forward.'}
{3: 'Yet, how can human legs outpace a surging tide?'}
{3: "It's like a nonchalant slaughter or a one-sided game—the viscous liquid chuckles as it envelops the ankles of the straggling refugees."}
{3: 'Hetero-Creatures arrive with the tide, cautiously inspecting the fallen humans, seemingly selecting their targets.'}
{3: 'Deep finger marks are imprinted in the soil as another refugee disappears into the tide.'}
{3: 'His bare feet touching the ground begin to burn—the Red Tide is already brushing against his ankles.'}
{2: 'Garry', 3: 'Gemira... Run!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'With a roar, he musters his final reserves of strength to lunge forward a few steps, pushing Gemira ahead.'}
{3: 'Warm tears streak down the rough skin of his cheeks, but Gemira dares not look back. He keeps running forward with all his might until...'}
{3: 'A cold liquid creeps over his feet.'}
{3: 'He collapses in despair, the stinging pain in his palm telling him that the Red Tide is gradually consuming the land.'}
{3: 'Everywhere his gaze lands, only hoarse cries of pain and whispers of despair linger.'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: 'Garry...'}
{3: 'In the muddy Red Tide, he struggles to crawl forward.'}
{2: 'Gemira', 3: "We can't just end like this... Ah..."}

{3: 'As a cold blue light slices through the crimson tide, the sound of car engines reaches his ears almost simultaneously with the noise of a transport craft touchdown, coming from various directions.'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Commandant! Someone's there!", 4: '1'}
